{"tid":57230,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"（重post)一個人遊塞舌爾六日五夜","createTime":"2016-12-27T23:53:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-29T15:14:42.000Z","uid":51268,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a997b4f689c474015d17742bb8fc9d7356f29ba8","tid":57230,"uid":51268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T23:53:32.000Z","msg":"之前係高登po過一次，得閒冇野做想po多次，今次會有小小唔同，唔知仲有冇巴打記得我呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一次一條友去旅行，英語又唔掂。當初真係有d驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （其實我老母仲驚過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ） <br />\n今次個旅程係：塞舌爾（6日5夜）+ 杜拜（5日4夜）8月29-9月8 <br />\n杜拜就唔打，反正好多人應該去過，主要講塞舌爾，比較冷門。詳情自己維基<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n阿聯酋航空，晚上7點50分起飛，香港》杜拜》馬埃島，六點到達。馬埃島》杜拜（停留5日）》香港，機票7千幾。 <br />\n<br />\nDay1:馬埃島 <br />\nDay2:馬埃島 <br />\nDay3:馬埃島（首都維多利亞） <br />\nDay:4普拉蘭島 <br />\nDay:5拉迪格島 <br />\nDay6:去杜拜 <br />\n<br />\n去杜拜轉機嘅時候，坐A380客機，機尾只有幾個人，可以一個人訓4個位zzzzzzz。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/28/075232_0944f1b33bc0f93b6789fe4aa8abd5ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F28%2F075232_0944f1b33bc0f93b6789fe4aa8abd5ec.jpg&h=0db05750&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在杜拜逗留三個鐘左右，行下免稅店、食下煙仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，到左登機時間，上到機先發現成架機好似得我一個黃皮膚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd98a0623d165f53e549458590afe97b41013df1","tid":57230,"uid":51268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T23:55:31.000Z","msg":"落機後，在入境大廳等左好耐，到左櫃台，個入境職員用英文問我問題，我聽唔明，就比人帶到去另一邊問話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，都係出示一下住宿、往返機票、過黎做咩、身上有幾多錢等等，行李仲要比海關搜遍，最後搞左成粒幾鐘先放我走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我走的時候，個海關望住我講：welcome to seychelles<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。出到機埸，換錢、搞sim卡。另外在塞舌爾租車、包車、旅行社報團等等比較大額的消費通常用歐元結算；買食物、日用品呢D低消費活動用盧比「SCR」。 <br />\n<br />\n基本需要嘅野都已經搞掂，跟住搭的士去住宿。雖然在網絡上做過功課，都知道呢邊嘅taxi 超貴，一程起碼30-50歐元左右，而且冇跳錶呢樣野嘅存在，最好上車前問清楚司機價錢。不過人生路不熟，加上已經好累想快d去訓教，揀左搭的士，最後不到三十分鐘的車程承惠600盧比（大約港幣350左右），到左住宿，已經朝早9點幾，同henry(民宿的老闆）傾左幾句後，就去左訓教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。 <br />\n<br />\n住宿出面的風景<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/28/075527_02fb00aa22769d0aa3bda6c9d706d5e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F28%2F075527_02fb00aa22769d0aa3bda6c9d706d5e7.jpg&h=24b27829&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"156acd76784fd524fec6bfa66663962eb333f812","tid":57230,"uid":51268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T23:58:33.000Z","msg":"下午五點幾起床後，想搵d野食下，henry就話山底下有間餐廳，行路廿分鐘左右就可以到，行左幾分鐘後，發現呢邊根本就冇街燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，太陽又快落山了，食完仲洗番上山咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，最後死死氣咁走番轉頭。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n回到住宿後，henry問做咩咁快番到黎，我話太陽就快落山，冇燈光食完點行番黎（當然用好爛嘅英文加身體語言講），佢話可以等我食完飯，7點左右係餐廳門口等佢揸車載我番去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢真係好好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n餐廳外嘅風景日落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/28/075733_00265b2b72a84fdea6453eecac23744a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F28%2F075733_00265b2b72a84fdea6453eecac23744a.jpg&h=cabc3633&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n塞舌爾嘅第一餐，除左雞肉好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，其他都唔係幾啱我口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/28/075803_17f19b7d976d2659b62625647f134cf1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F28%2F075803_17f19b7d976d2659b62625647f134cf1.jpg&h=9f824326&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n回去後，同henry 傾左陣，當中唔少對話都要出動google翻譯同指手劃腳，不過佢都好熱心咁介紹有咩地方好玩、吹下水咁，完全冇唔耐煩嘅感覺，仲幫我打電話租車。原來佢係塞舌爾印裔，仲識講印度語。"},{"pid":"8fa5aac4f3fe59de339261d0978a133c909b8bfd","tid":57230,"uid":51268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T00:01:57.000Z","msg":"Day:2 <br />\n塞舌爾租車方便，我租車5日用左200歐元，油費唔貴，租車只要比租金，唔需要比按金，還車時在約好嘅地點把車匙放在車內嘅腳毯下就可以走人，不過千祈唔好鎖門。租車公司嘅職員會同你一齊睇下架車邊到有刮花。租車唔洗國際牌用香港車牌就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。塞舌爾主要道路是山路，同香港一樣靠左行，大部分道路只有兩條行車線。 <br />\n<br />\n我租嘅車<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPXTKtgd427Bm2CUdMGHQppkNUyjAkxiqiw5zZjBxpNfM?filename=H42x9n2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH42x9n2.jpg&h=9bc2664f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實我甩左p冇幾耐，考左個牌番黎完全冇揸過車，今次係考完牌第一次揸車，仲要係山路，唔好彩真係連人帶車飛落山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係搭巴士又唔方便，搭的士又貴，焗住要租車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n攞左車之後，去博瓦隆海灘，塞舌爾除左市中心之外，d車基本上亂泊，隨便泊係個草地上就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 海灘的人不多，在沙灘上曬下太陽、散步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。 <br />\n<br />\n沙灘風景<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVxLMLEntqGHmHYgwrg3mg4jkxo53ME3XmQhBWwSUJsqh?filename=1721CN5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1721CN5.jpg&h=a66bff05&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/28/080141_b17858950571411b8f4f45ff50eb71df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F28%2F080141_b17858950571411b8f4f45ff50eb71df.jpg&h=eaed159d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVZ1eDB2j3Avp6aUty6pewP7NN5n2d6r8L7XtQaQGkfsb?filename=6F38767.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6F38767.jpg&h=b2d0c17c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/28/080142_cc1bfa26e3e215a4793d57f7fe751199.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F28%2F080142_cc1bfa26e3e215a4793d57f7fe751199.jpg&h=bae75367&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71715b81b69d5c81e454bb21b8b576c487c54898","tid":57230,"uid":51268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T00:15:08.000Z","msg":"Day:3 <br />\n<br />\n首都維多利亞，因為係市中心呢到人比較多，雖然係市中心，但係冇咩高樓大廈，暫時見到最高都係得5-6層左右。 <br />\n<br />\n街景圖 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/28/080424_282728c3e64ebfbff744d76d4858ada0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F28%2F080424_282728c3e64ebfbff744d76d4858ada0.jpg&h=f972a897&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n塞舌爾治安總體唔錯，係到咁多日起碼冇試過比人偷野同老笠，買野都冇比人抬高個價，可能係抬高左都覺得個價錢接受到，比人呃左都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n街上嘅人見到我呢個黃種人都用奇異的眼光望我，有d仲會主動同你打招呼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不斷問china、china？，我就不斷Hong kong Hong kong  fuck fuck <br />\n<br />\n大部分衣服、日用品都係made in china ，有幾個商場，不過都好殘舊，我行過咁多間商店，發現呢個國家好多商店都係冇冷氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 熱到想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過都唔夠杜拜40幾度咁熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n買左個唔知咩豬肉炒飯，好撚難食，食剩半個用黎喂雀算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n附近有間印度教嘅神廟（濕婆神），喜歡佛教嘅可以進去睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n神廟 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVSSFjQj7zUc8u2ArKbxQYGxWZWesa65t3KWdxQzF6Jbf?filename=8E8M9pY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8E8M9pY.jpg&h=4c465a3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n維多利亞嘅大笨鐘，聽講係以前英國殖民地時期留低嘅野黎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRNswkXwDpMsqqHrkxrAtA6XC6HPodauyGxj5fyiQJzxj?filename=95vgGZ1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F95vgGZ1.jpg&h=2a8d726d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本身打算去搵一間旅行社join團去玩，跟住google map路線去行，點知越走越出市區，走左去冇咩人嘅地方，跟住比兩隻狗咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咬完之後，我即刻衝番到住宿到清毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbfgRwVhkpD2m6EBbNxFCtdjkYtKjvs2LhgFnhbBgSMyn?filename=5XE641q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5XE641q.jpg&h=79f55c7f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaJTTTE5cTbPeeuYfdDhVzkSL6FQqhVhpnLcrMZPfqjSr?filename=72091G3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F72091G3.jpg&h=8d0e9203&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個咬一個抓，兩隻狗都好撚狠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，第二朝起身個傷口都仲流緊小小血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，不過番到香港都打左瘋狗疫苗。"},{"pid":"42c6939a7d07ac0247f45d973e5f16fdb1df63b4","tid":57230,"uid":51268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T00:22:55.000Z","msg":"Day:4 <br />\n坐小型飛機到普拉蘭島<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTEezZtPoR5NYfW1tiwmgcbUzXAe6jPhYtpgDV7cMn4Ud?filename=2DcC845.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2DcC845.jpg&h=b78000e1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/28/081814_652cea8c0cde13ea8919d0cac0a9e6f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F28%2F081814_652cea8c0cde13ea8919d0cac0a9e6f0.jpg&h=37ae5790&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/28/081814_ec5a715d12e9e0f6926f75bcaecc5abf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F28%2F081814_ec5a715d12e9e0f6926f75bcaecc5abf.jpg&h=c8bd4588&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/28/081815_99d2e5022ae620494a675b97a7e2591b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F28%2F081815_99d2e5022ae620494a675b97a7e2591b.jpg&h=55cadf4f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/28/081816_99d2e5022ae620494a675b97a7e2591b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F28%2F081816_99d2e5022ae620494a675b97a7e2591b.jpg&h=b68368ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到世界自然遺產五月谷，門票40歐元，喜歡植物的可以入去參觀一下，入面真係冇咩睇，比40歐元大部分都係睇樹，感覺好似呃錢fuck<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/28/081923_d95b06eccfb259b87c12cc2ee29852d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F28%2F081923_d95b06eccfb259b87c12cc2ee29852d2.jpg&h=0b39b757&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUmVJYNEpTJ54zpxbCozUTBAojjVAQazyXD5Uxm2XxFW8?filename=gMYhmV7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgMYhmV7.jpg&h=a7939a5c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/28/081925_103664f10868570fcf177cd699073b3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F28%2F081925_103664f10868570fcf177cd699073b3c.jpg&h=7e1f4d8d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/28/081926_103664f10868570fcf177cd699073b3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F28%2F081926_103664f10868570fcf177cd699073b3c.jpg&h=9d56fa2f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYZtu2PXzrjg1GNn5YHKQdfCWVt8BPKgX9JRvqHp9QRXM?filename=O636kaK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO636kaK.jpg&h=508f145d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n塞舌爾的國寶 海椰子<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbefkniHozTRnduRW7U5Enzn3KnLCWNhXa3RbEpMoFTUh?filename=40BwfQ0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F40BwfQ0.jpg&h=d7e18e38&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXDYt6NmrsL5T9zHXxJSykCsPMyWBzUAwNvYZhk8cwLsi?filename=f5AdSwQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff5AdSwQ.jpg&h=2f515051&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係裡面見到一班小學生，我估應該係學校搞嘅活動之類入黎參觀，啲小黑見到我，又係用好奇嘅眼光望住我，然後同我講give me five，之後十幾個人排住隊咁同我擊掌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成個公園行左唔夠一粒鍾就出左黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n來到拉齊奧海灘，海水通透的藍色，比起馬埃島博瓦隆海灘，我覺得呢到係最觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 海灘好長，附近有不少酒店。 <br />\n<br />\n拉齊奧海灘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmddX2fRBQQYnEV2cB9ueuA74XhKQqgr7mS5fcxZeRHiTu?filename=K63491j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK63491j.jpg&h=eb20574c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/28/082127_9be137e5be20cc71fe48e3fc747cec12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F28%2F082127_9be137e5be20cc71fe48e3fc747cec12.jpg&h=923b4568&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/28/082127_377048c6e964b0612e0e6d5021d918e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F28%2F082127_377048c6e964b0612e0e6d5021d918e9.jpg&h=68fba96e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/28/082128_377048c6e964b0612e0e6d5021d918e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F28%2F082128_377048c6e964b0612e0e6d5021d918e9.jpg&h=b076ccc6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmd6Ubbu6DMXaSbnSSmbjNwW8prkd4pwrz9W9PTDTdiBgz?filename=bmm8P2s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbmm8P2s.jpg&h=ce8a7aac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天氣唔係咁好，搞到影出黎唔係好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n海灘的酒店<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/28/082208_1720de1e4080b7336ab67a93a0375329.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F28%2F082208_1720de1e4080b7336ab67a93a0375329.jpg&h=b8afd711&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTiAWrkyz2APZHKsJQVRSxewdemutkfjyG9VCnfN4c5KN?filename=Qxi29yF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQxi29yF.jpg&h=eda48288&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有好多鬼佬黎呢到度密月或者一家大細過黎玩，每個人隔離都有條鬼妹陪佢曬太陽、游水，相反得我自己一個，i know that feel brothers<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n坐飛機番馬埃島check in 的時候，佢話我遲到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，4點半起飛我4點10分check in都當遲到fuck ，仲以為坐小型飛機唔洗咁早黎添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，好彩都幫我改左5點半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，如果唔係就要搭船番去要用1個鐘，坐飛機先10-20分鐘。 <br />\n<br />\n機場門口的噴水池<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcSNhF4HaTmYy3oPQngHp6GeYcQ9BkxH4CL9vHeB9giMg?filename=M262kw1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM262kw1.jpg&h=bb680857&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ad76290e710528ab25574d30c4136819de88776","tid":57230,"uid":51268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T00:35:54.000Z","msg":"Day:5 <br />\n<br />\n打算揸車去碼頭搭船去拉迪格島，點知天雨路滑，唔小心撞左落防撞欄到，撞花左架車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，好彩有防撞欄，唔係就炒左落山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，算是不幸中的大幸。最後係機場還車的時候，放低400歐元就走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmU7hgK2HT6dRvfeoES8M8Cfy9Q2kbnzsipAicFWjnxmFN?filename=vdV8wX8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvdV8wX8.jpg&h=43819c11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到左碼頭後，船速快加上有啲晃，有暈船的人請做好心理準備。 <br />\n<br />\n下船後，租左架單車150盧比。 <br />\n踏住單車周圍遊下，我覺得呢邊嘅風景比馬埃島同普拉蘭島仲靚，附近有間教堂，有人係到結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/28/083125_4bccc2b6da01c192666a23c7287d3b78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F28%2F083125_4bccc2b6da01c192666a23c7287d3b78.jpg&h=298463cf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmb3azENrcq8J7xaDs1vELdTZ7xct7ATNX5z819Dm5Fdop?filename=8d9pjc3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8d9pjc3.jpg&h=dcb07db2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/28/083126_5dbcf8db7e685d6384a4b145777c0618.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F28%2F083126_5dbcf8db7e685d6384a4b145777c0618.jpg&h=c99bab11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n牛車 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNZQcUXTMhVzAaVz7m1WMKvxS9hPpXwqkHodhiDfDZxLm?filename=9H2290H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9H2290H.jpg&h=7f0ba7d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去德阿讓海灘的路上，一定要經過一個象龜養殖埸，門票要100盧比，感覺有小小呃錢。 <br />\n塞舌爾的國寶 象龜 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/28/083304_2db89150c1a8a3dc6b44b266f31048d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F28%2F083304_2db89150c1a8a3dc6b44b266f31048d3.jpg&h=61293936&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdcRdgiU5hygAdt61rz15jcAfUJJ7ksS4xiXnZe6V6wMN?filename=q9CU592.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq9CU592.jpg&h=27867ebf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/28/083305_ebf7a5481e6bffa0b1b9f4c640543215.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F28%2F083305_ebf7a5481e6bffa0b1b9f4c640543215.jpg&h=29e35602&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/28/083306_ebf7a5481e6bffa0b1b9f4c640543215.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F28%2F083306_ebf7a5481e6bffa0b1b9f4c640543215.jpg&h=caaae1a0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmbssh5Dw7qi5NcrbEfgtiDjXjP5rMb6TQdSJAs2vjhZ7p?filename=b16VY0S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb16VY0S.jpg&h=3964d600&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n影得唔係幾好，其實有半個人咁大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n象龜都超大超重，如果不小心比佢踩一腳，估計幾日行路會拐下拐下，見到有啲人會坐上去，隻龜仲行得到，聽講有隻年齡最大已經143歲，一百年前，晚清先出世。撿啲樹葉，佢地喜歡食呢個 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZA6iZwBjes9drPuRsKcTC7yAY9aJsmvKYh4TZmSC1xrn?filename=y96t532.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy96t532.jpg&h=7a0a4ce4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQ2VRchzzwg1ivBWXSaJM3U8Se5q2Yuh2wspm3KpndRvy?filename=Ew8i35T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEw8i35T.jpg&h=5891fe45&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVrURWNCKMmc8sEoyFroiEZQqicDBX8NVse1c1u12b9v4?filename=U0145s9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU0145s9.jpg&h=3b2640c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到了德阿讓海灘，被世界攝影愛好者評選為排名第一，人不多，有啲人係到浮潛。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXAvWMNgiRVzGu3X17UZGDXMQiCA2XUemm5sArXPFffSk?filename=BuhQUrv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBuhQUrv.jpg&h=2e8b6e49&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcLXPYrQqaivoCUJHbjPTJrfLbvB8QaQFZNRKeZjR7q8D?filename=3U809H5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3U809H5.jpg&h=90620fc7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/28/083512_31a37503d10de2fe315939ac6ff21d04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F28%2F083512_31a37503d10de2fe315939ac6ff21d04.jpg&h=9ad32f95&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/28/083512_d4218e0bbc206d8c20566b735422fad1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F28%2F083512_d4218e0bbc206d8c20566b735422fad1.jpg&h=3c122a98&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeNg36KTzrZHeRuw1dqrWZMTPXX1NNXHvY2bXQ1qi4FWg?filename=4ijeQwb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4ijeQwb.jpg&h=dd9ef57e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n連狗都要落水玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYsC4yritdbxD84iELhhH9scrUABvECoUELEtBgj6sk2e?filename=TWxM1v0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTWxM1v0.jpg&h=a13f62b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eb5f02e5c0c72bd97e64d5c40331b1f759d5e01","tid":57230,"uid":50395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T00:50:03.000Z","msg":"做乜無啦啦俾狗咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f939473c2859cc7a595ac047f79da65c15bb2ae","tid":57230,"uid":51268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T00:53:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做乜無啦啦俾狗咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n運氣唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01cd74f431ea257d1ee6fe8ff2b7e66396581d2a","tid":57230,"uid":50395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T00:59:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做乜無啦啦俾狗咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n運氣唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打好勁 好勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fed20f78d24f84f51114baa739e07ff9ddd06f56","tid":57230,"uid":7789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T01:09:59.000Z","msg":"想問巴打用左幾錢？"},{"pid":"90d92259bbbdd2b1e875734307cfc77ff4fb6d5f","tid":57230,"uid":51268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T01:15:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問巴打用左幾錢？</blockquote><br />\n應該千幾歐左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3da98058fbb5b6c0fe13fa6d446799549c08b6d","tid":57230,"uid":51268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T13:48:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class